title: Yat-Kha, Mongolian Rock from Tuva with throat singing, 6 albums
description:
Here comes Yat-Kha, the most famous rock band from Tuva, reknown for its lead singer and his amazing throat singing. If you don&#039;t know them yet, you really should check them out.

The albums are:
Yenisei Punk (1995), debut album for Yat-Kha as a rock band
Tundra&#039;s Ghosts (1997), more electronic remixes by Ivan Sokolovsky
Dalai Beldiri (1999)
Aldyn Dashka (2000)
tuva.rock (2003)
ReCovers (2005), covers of rock band in the unique style of Yat-Kha, you gotta listen to that!

Enjoy
